<div class="ux-design w-full flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between text-[#fbfbfb]">
  <h2>UX & Design Strategy</h2>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 md:gap-3 md:w-1/2">
    <p class="text-xs md:text-base">
      Conducted design audit to identify inconsistencies, visual fragility,
      and missing responsive behaviors
    </p>
    <p class="text-xs md:text-base">
      Rebuilt missing user flows (e.g. trade history, exposure, account
      verification, leaderboard)
    </p>
    <p class="text-xs md:text-base">
      Designed visual system: clean dark/neutral base theme, consistent
      typography, spacing, iconography, color coding (buy/sell, exposure,
      risk)
    </p>
    <p class="text-xs md:text-base -mt-4">
      Ensured that design files were structured (auto layout, use of tokens)
      and ready for development handoff
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .ux-design {
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .ux-design h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 100;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
</style>